data.text:
Architect: George Semple

An elevation of Essex Bridge, later Grattan Bridge in Dublin, as rebuilt by George Semple in 1755. Begun 19 Jan 1753, and finished 11 May 1755. The East Elevation and Section of the Foundation of Essex Bridge, Dublin, engrd. plate, c. 1760, approx.
